# StarcallOS environment — DEV CONVENIENCE ONLY.
#
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) if you want `pnpm dev` to pick up an LLM key
# without opening the in-app Settings panel. These values are read at RUNTIME by
# the main process and are NEVER inlined into a packaged build, so they cannot
# leak inside a shipped .exe. In a real install, keys live in the OS-encrypted
# settings file (safeStorage), not here.
#
# Extraction works with zero keys; only enrichment and grading need one.

# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
